<plot>Hannes, rejected from his Ex-girlfriend for the second time, finds himself lost in the streets. His rescue seems to be the idea of a Pizza delivery to his house he taking the ride with it- but Hannes did not bargain for the stubborn female driver. His nightly journey ends in obscure and life breaking situations. The short won several audience awards and was shown at the famous Filmfestival Max Ophuels Festival 2006/ Gain "Praedikat wertvoll" from FDB Germany.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?434287</url></doc>
